  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Fixes coder/internal#1287\n\n`TestBackedPipe_DuplicateReconnectionPrevention` was a CI flake due to relying on goroutine scheduling around concurrent `ForceReconnect()` calls. Making it fully deterministic without changing production code would require `unsafe`/reflection-style introspection into `x/sync/singleflight` internals, which we consider unacceptable.\n\nThis PR removes the flaky test (and its now-unused blocking reconnector helper).\n\n## Testing\n- `go test ./agent/immortalstreams/backedpipe`\n- `make lint`\n",
